To improve the performance of your MySQL container based on the provided mysqlslap benchmarking details, consider adjusting the following parameters:

```json
[
    "innodb_buffer_pool_size",
    "innodb_log_file_size",
    "innodb_log_buffer_size",
    "innodb_flush_log_at_trx_commit",
    "max_connections",
    "thread_cache_size",
    "query_cache_size",
    "table_open_cache",
    "tmp_table_size"
]
```
